name: DVI-I MALE TO DVI-I FEMALE ADAPTOR
description:
DVI-I MALE TO DVI-I FEMALE ADAPTOR-DVI020

Digital Visual Interface (DVI)

The digital interface is used to connect a video source,

Such as a display controller to a display device, such as a computer monitor

It was developed with the intention of creating an industry

Standard for the transfer of digital video content

The interface is designed to transmit uncompressed digital

Video and can be configured to support multiple modes such as DVI-D (digital only)

DVI-A (analog only), or DVI-I (digital and analog)

Featuring support for analog connections

The DVI specification is compatible with the VGA interface

This compatibility, along with other advantages

Led to its widespread acceptance over competing digital display

Standards Plug and Display (P&D) and Digital Flat Panel (DFP)

Although DVI is predominantly associated with computers

It is sometimes used in other consumer electronics such as television sets

Video game consoles needs citation and DVD players

(NVMe) M.2, 1 x SATA III M.2 - PCIe 3.0

This 2-Port M.2 SSD Adapter card is one of the only Cards that Supports both PCIe and SATA-based M.2 SSDs

Increase The Storage Of Your Desktop PC

This Card Provides a Platform for Adding up to Two M.2 SSDs To Virtually any Computer That has A PCIe Slot

It Supports common M.2 SATA SSDs, as well as newer High-Performance M.2 PCIe Drives

Now you have a simple and effective way to Expand the Storage of your Computer, regardless of the M.2 Drive Types you are using

name: AI TRACKING GIMBAL
description:
AI TRACKING GIMBAL - SMT001

Product Name: 360 Degree Al Tracking Gimbal

Product Model: JS008

Load: 800g

Net Weight: 270g (include lithium-ion battery)

Product Size: 118*67mm

Phone Size acceptable: <7.0"

Mechanical Angle: Horizontal 350 deg

Working Angle: 6H

Power Supply Mode: USB+lithium-ion battery

Input Voltage: 5V 1A

Compatible to Android & IOS Systems iOS: ios10.0

Usage Scenario

There are two scenario: one is put on the desk, the other is put on tripod

There is no need for other settings if you to use it on desk

If you need to use tripod , please put tripod into tripod base and turn the base to tight

Turn on /off

This device has built in battery , we advise you to charge it for 6 hours before use it

Open the mobile holder, put your mobile (tablet) to adjust the holder

Hold the power button for 5 seconds, it will turn on, the indicator lamp will blink and the device will rotate one circle

If you need to turn off , please hold the power button 5 seconds again

How to use

Make sure the holder is tighten your mobile (tablet) before starting it , it will start tracking human face (body)

The best distance to use is 1-5 meters

About indicator lamp

There are 3 different mode of indicator lamp means different status of battery

The RED indicator lamp is off means the battery is full

The RED indicator lamp is blinking rapidly means battery low, need to charge the battery

The RED indicator lamp is blinking slowly means under charging

Note

Built -  in battery inside, do not put it in high temperature (over 50 deg C) or humidity environment

Use hand to rotate gimbal is not allowed

It can only track one human face (body) it is not recommended to use it when there are two or more people

Please charge the device in time when the indicator lamp is blinking red and make sure the adapter is 5V1A ( or 5V2A)

To avoid the device working wrong

description:

CS-DL05

Smart Fingerprint Lock

Enjoy Easy Keyless Entry Of A Safe Home

The DL05 Sticks to the core values of a truly Smart Lock

Or pets from accidentally opening the Door from the inside

You can also enable its privacy mode if you dont want to be disturbed

Then only the Administrator can open the Door from the Outside

name: DMS 59 PIN TO 2XVGA SPLITTER
description:
DMS 59 PIN TO 2XVGA SPLITTER-DMS59-VGA

MicroWorld DMS Male To 2X Female Splitter

DMS-59 (Dual Monitor Solution, 59 pins) is Generally used for Computer Video Cards

It Provides two DVI or VGA Outputs in a Single Connector

An Adapter Cable is Needed for Conversion from DMS-59 (digital) to DVI (digital) or VGA (analog)

And Different types of Adapter Cables Exist

The Connector is four Pins High and 15 Pins Wide, with a Single Pin Missing from the Bottom Row

In a D-shaped shell, with Thumbscrew

The Advantage of DMS-59 is its ability to support two high resolution displays

Such as two DVI Single Link digital channels or two VGA analog channels, in a single DVI-size connector

Compact size lets a half-height Card Support two high Resolution Displays,

And a full-height Card (with two DMS-59 connectors) up to four High Resolution Displays

The DMS-59 Connector is used by ATI, NVIDIA, and Matrox for Video Cards Sold in Lenovo Thinkcentres

Viglen Genies and Omninos, Dell, HP, and Sun Computers

Some Confusion has been Caused by the fact that Vendors label Cards with DMS-59 as supports DVI

But the Cards have no DVI Connectors Built-in

Such cards, when Equipped with only a VGA Connector Adapter Cable

Cannot be Connected to a Monitor with only a DVI-D Input

A DMS-59 to DVI Adapter cable needs to be used with such Monitors

The DMS-59 Connector is Derived from the Molex Low Force Helix Connector

Which could be found in some earlier Graphics Cards

These ports are similar to DMS-59, but have all 60 pins present, whereas DMS-59 has one pin (pin 58) blocked

A connector plug with all 60 pins (such as a Molex 88766-7610 DVI-I splitter) does not fit into a properly keyed DMS-59 socket

name: BNC TO HDMI CONVERTOR
description:
BNC TO HDMI CONVERTOR - BNC2HDMI

BNC to HDMI Converter, Composite BNC and Audio Input to HDMI Output Adapter with 720P/1080P Switch

Transfer Analog Video Signal from CCTV Security Camera to HD Monitor Projector Computer

FUNCTIONS

The Video Converters is a must-have to keep older devices with new modern PC Monitor or LCD

It takes a connect from CVBS Security Camera directly to an HDMI TV

Or Converts old Security System DVR Output

(Analog Video Signal) to HDMI (Digital Video Signal) for Flat Screen Monitor

COMPATIBILITY

This box composites CVBS BNC Analog Video Signal Input

And 3.5mm Aux Audio Signal Input to HDMI Output with a 720P/1080P Switch.

NOTE:

It's only for CVBS Analog Camera, can NOT fit the Digital Camera or AHD/TVI/CVI Camera

The Output Port is standard HDMI Type A

It's NOT an SDI Converter, can NOT Convert Cable TV signal

Don't use it to connect your Antenna and Cable TV

SPECIFICATION

The Adapter adapts 3D Compensation Technology:

Motion optimization, color Optimization and Digital noise reduction

Automatically detects Input Signals in PAL or NTSC format, Supports 720P@50/60Hz

1080P@50/60Hz HDMI Output Resolution (The resolution can reach up to 1920 x 1080 on LED LCTV)

freely switch between 4:3 and 16:9 modes

FEATURES

It has an exclusive 3.5mm Audio Port to Input Audible Signals

Which allows you to inject sounds to the CVBS Cameras Video Signals

The low-power-consumption Digital chip enables the Adapter to work 24-hour 

Uninterruptedly and stablely with low heat releasing

It's a simplistic way to broadcast live Video feed and perfect for real-time Video Monitor using CVBS protocol

PLUG and PLAY

Wire it as follows, CVBS CCTV Camera or DVR with BNC Output - Coax Cable

This Adapter - HDMI Cable - PC Monitor/ Projector/ Computer

Work after easy installation without any special settings, no driver Software required

NOTE

If you use a TV set as the Monitor, switch the Input or source button on the TV clicker to the HMID mode

name: DVI CABLE M-M 3.0 M
description:
DVI CABLE M-M 3.0 M - CAB015

Digital Visual Interface (DVI)

The digital interface is used to connect a video source

Such as a display controller to a display device

Such as a computer monitor

It was developed with the intention of creating

An industry standard for the transfer of digital video content

The interface is designed to transmit uncompressed digital

Video and can be configured to support multiple modes such as DVI-D (digital only)

DVI-A (analogue only), or DVI-I (digital and antilog)

Featuring support for analogue connections, 

The DVI specification is compatible with the VGA interface

This compatibility, along with other advantages

Led to its widespread acceptance over competing digital

Display standards Plug and Display (P&D) and Digital Flat Panel (DFP)

Although DVI is predominantly associated with computers

It is sometimes used in other consumer electronics such as television sets

Video game consoles needs citation and DVD players

3.0 Meter Cable

name: DVI-DVI(24+1) 5M CABLE
description:
DVI-DVI(24+1) 5M CABLE- DVI003

Digital Visual Interface (DVI)

The digital interface is used to connect a video source,

Such as a display controller to a display device, such as a computer monitor

It was developed with the intention of creating an industry

Standard for the transfer of digital video content

The interface is designed to transmit uncompressed digital

Video and can be configured to support multiple modes such as DVI-D (digital only)

DVI-A (analog only), or DVI-I (digital and analog).

Featuring support for analog connections,

The DVI specification is compatible with the VGA interface

This compatibility, along with other advantages,

Led to its widespread acceptance over competing digital display standards Plug and Display (P&D) and

Digital Flat Panel (DFP).Although DVI is predominantly associated with computers,

It is sometimes used in other consumer electronics such as television sets

Video game consoles needs citation and DVD players

-5.0 Meter Cable

-DVI-D Male To Male

Enabling easier Game loading and small files Transmission

With the major update to 4.0, this PCIe Version dramatically increases the Bandwidth available

Significantly increasing the potential of what the connected Hardware can do

Equipped with a formidable PCIe 4.0 Controller and quality Flash

Predator GM7 boasts an excellent Speed of 2400 MT/s.

MORE USABLE CAPACITY, LONGER LIFESPAN

Featuring quality NAND, Predator GM7 provides a whopping Performance and a longer lifespan

Predator GM7 offers a larger capacity to meet your storage requirements

MORE EFFECTIVE POWER MANAGEMENT

Predator GM7 adopts a 12 nm Power-Saving Controller

Thermal Throttling, and Power Management to overcome typical heating issues, an efficient solution even under a heavy workload

FREE ACRONIS CLONING, SEAMLESS DATA TRANSFER

With our free Customized Version of Acronis True Image

Consumers have access to Seamless Data Transfer and Backup

This Cloning Software is able to restore System functions in a natural disaster

Or emergency to ensure Data preservation, Security and Privacy

FITS ALL YOUR DEVICES PERFECTLY

GM7's single-sided PCB fits your Desktop and Laptop perfectly for your System Upgrade

It can serve as the Drive of your choice of most Devices

EXTREMELY DURABLE SSD WITH 5-YEAR WARRANTY

Predator GM7 is built with strict tests to provide exceptionally robust quality and guaranteed TBW

Chipset Description:

The IP100A is a single-chip, full duplex, 10/100Mbps Ethernet MAC + PHY incorporating a 32-bit PCI with bus master support

The IP100A is designed for use in a variety of applications including workstation NICs, PC motherboards, and

Other systems utilizing a PCI bus that require network connectivity to an Ethernet or Fast Ethernet LAN.

The IP100A includes a PCI bus interface unit, IEEE 802.3 compliant MAC, transmit and receive FIFO buffers

IEEE 802.3 compliant 100BASE-TX, 10BASE-T, and 100BASE-FX PHY, serial 

EEPROM interface, expansion ROM interface, and LED drivers

The IP100A implements a rich set of control and status registers

Accessible via the PCI interface, these registers provide a host system visibility into the features 

And operating state of the IP100A

Network management statistics are also recorded

And host access to registers of the PHY device are facilitated through the IP100A's PCI interface

The IP100A supports features for use in "Green PCs" or systems where control over system power consumption is desired

The IP100A supports several power down states, and the ability to issue a system

Wake event" via reception of unique user defined Ethernet frames

In addition, the IP100A can assert a wake event in response to changes in the Ethernet link status

Features:

Single chip 10/100BASE, half or full duplex Ethernet Media Access Controller

IEEE 802.3 compliant 100BASE-TX/100BASE-FX/10BSE-T

PCI Bus master scatter/gather DMA on any byte boundary

Full operation with PCI Clock from 25 MHz to 33 MHz

PCI Revision 2.2 compliant

On-chip transmit and receive FIFO buffers

On-chip LED drivers

Power management capabilities for ACPI 1.0 compliant systems

WakeOnLAN support

Management statistics gathering

IP multicast receive and filter support using 64 bit hash table

Transmit polling

Auto pad insertion for short packets

Programmable minimum Inter Packet Gap

Programmable transmit and receive FIFO watermarks

Smart Cable Analyzer (SCA) Support

Capable of using 93C46 or 93C56 EEPROM

On-chip crystal oscillator

On-chip voltage regulator

2.5/3.3V CMOS with 5V tolerant I/O

0.25µm technology

128-pin PQFP

description:
PREDATOR VESTA2 32GB PC5 6800 SILVER - BL.9BWWR.361

Acer Predator Vesta II RGB DDR5 Memory

Up to 7200 MHz, Supports XMP 3.0, On-Die ECC

High-Quality ICs

Speeds up to 7200 MHz

Supports XMP 3.0 & AMD EXPO

PUSH THE BOUNDARIES WITH VESTA II DDR5 MEMORY

Take your Gaming and Computer experience to new heights with the latest Generation of DDR: Predator Vesta II DDR5 lets you run at MAX 7200 MHz

It's blazing fast but also a top-notch performer with sleek design

Ultra-low timings, Customizable RGB lighting and stylish metallic Heat Sink

Built with Quality Components, Vesta II DDR5 features on-die Error Correction

HIGH SPEED 7200 MHZ BRINGS YOU TO NEW HEIGHTS

Whether it's Gaming, Metaverse, or Computer-intensive content creation, today you need as much Speed as you can get

Predator Vesta II brings DDR5 Performance to any tough game or task

HAND-SORTED ICS ENSURE ULTRA-LOW TIMINGS

Vesta II is built with Quality Components to ensure top-notch Performance

For example, Vesta II DDR5-7200 with a low latency of CL34 really hits the sweet spot for High Speed and tight timings

With Quality in mind, Predator provides you the Vesta II only after undergoing rigorous tests to take whatever punishment you throw at it

PLAYS WELL WITH TOP TIER MOTHERBOARDS & CPUS

With hand-Screened ICs, Vesta II brings faster-than-ever speed to your top Motherboards and CPUs

From the default 4800 MHz, you can take off at 7200 MHz with XMP open

Unleash new potential with overclocking on Vesta II REFRESH YOUR RGB STYLE

The upgraded Vesta II Memory Module features brighter lighting and more pure lighting effects

Featuring customizable RGB lighting through Supported Mainstream Motherboard Software

You can select from a dozen of stunning lighting effects to create your own style with nearly-limitless customization

DDR5 MORE THAN DOUBLES DATA PROCESSING BANDWIDTH

The New Generation of DDR is more of a big jump than a step forward

Boosted by doubling the banks and the burst length

And Featuring two independent 32-Bit Subchannels

Vesta II's outstanding handling of Bandwidth and Data enables faster-than-ever-before rendering, Processing, and Buffering

STYLISH HEAT SPREADER WITH SENSOR FOR REAL-TIME MONITORING

Vesta II's stylish Metallic Heat Sink comes with visually-pleasing tilted grooves on its Surface to enhance convection and effectively dissipate heat

With its built-in Temperature Sensor, Users can conduct real-time Monitoring

On-Die ERROR-CORRECTION TO STOP DATA CORRUPTION

Predator Vesta II Features an on-die ECC (Error Correcting Code) to Automatically detect and correct Memory Errors and fight Data corruption

While you push the limits, on-die ECC helps maintain Data integrity to sustain the ultimate Performance for Overclocking

PROGRAMMABLE PMIC IMPROVES SYSTEM STABILITY

Vesta II DDR5 comes with Programmable Power Management IC (PMIC) to save new User-Customizable Profiles

To achieve more efficient Power Load Management, and to improve the stability of Operations

XMP 3.0, THE LATEST FOR ONE-CLICK OVERCLOCKING

Programmed with the latest Intel XMP 3.0, the only thing between you and extreme Performance is a click

Just one-click and go. XMP 3.0 enables three factory pre-set Profiles that provides Users with more options for Overclocking

And two Customizable User-defined Profiles can be saved in the Memory Module via BIOS on Supported Motherboards

Your fine-tuned-Memory settings can go wherever the Modules go

name: 2 PORT HDMI SPLITTER
description:
2 PORT HDMI SPLITTER - 1IN2OUTHDMI

FY1409E 1 x 2 HDMI 4K x 2K Splitter

This 1 x 2 HDMI Splitter use a single HDMI source, accessing to multiple HDMI sinks

It allows one HDMI Device to be Split easily to four HDMI Compatible Monitors or Projectors

In addition,It can also be placed at the end of a long HDMI Cable to regenerate the HDMI Signal

The Resolution of this HDMI Splitter can be up to 3840 x 2160/30HZ

Features 

Support HDMI 1.4b Version

Support 3D Video Format

Support High Resolution up to 3840 x 2160/30HZ

Support Highest Rate of 3.2 G and TMDS Clock can be up to 320 MHz 

Support 8/10/12 Bit deep color

Support AWG26 HDMI Standard Cable: Input up to 15 Meters, Output up to 25 meters

 (when the Resolution is 4K, Input up to 12 Meters, Output up to 15 Meters)

Support one single HDMI source accessing to multiple HDMI sinks

The source can be DVD Player, A/V receiver, set top box and etc.

5V/2A Power Adapter

Specifications:                                   

Specifications:                                   

HDMI Version: HDMI 1.4b

HDMI Resolution: Up to 3840 x 2160/30Hz

Support Video Format: 8/10/12 bit deep color

Support Audio Format: DTS-HD/Dolby-true HD/DTS/Dolby-AC3/DSD

Max Bandwidth: 320MHz

Max Band Rate: 3.2Gbps

Input Cable Distance: (1080p resolution) =15m, (4K resolution)=12m AWG26 HDMI standard cable

Output Cable Distance: (1080p resolution) =25m, (4K resolution)=15m AWG26 HDMI standard cable

Max Working Current: 500mA

Power Adapter Format: Input AC (50HZ, 60HZ) 100V-240V; output: DC5V/2A

Operating Temperature Range:  (-15 to +55?)

Dimension (L x W x H): 178x66x20 (mm)

Weight: 220g

Connection and Operation

Connect the HD source to the Splitter input with one HDMI Cable

Connect the splitter output to the displays with 4 HDMI Cables

Connect 5V/2A Power Adapter to the Splitter

Package Include

HDMI Splitter 

Power Adapter

User Manual

This backpack is not just about looks; it seamlessly combines functionality with a touch of feline fun.

With this charming blue backpack, you can carry your essentials in style, all while showcasing your love for bear and playful aesthetics.

name: 8 WAY SERIAL PORT  SPLITTER
description:
8 WAY SERIAL PORT SPLITTER - RS108

RS 232 SERIAL SPL ITTER

Application

RS232 Serial Splitter is widely used in a variety of small and medium- sized Multimedia Conference Room

The Central Control System

The Serial Splitter Product is Designed to solve the problem of such Engineering Applications

Users can use the Device will be an RS232 Interface Extended to 4 or 8 Port

Suitable for the need for RS232 Communication Port Expansion of the Engineering Application System

Pin Definition 

Output Port Adopting DR9 Male

Pin is defined as: 3-Pin Transmit, 2-Pin Receive, 5-Pin Ground (That is, Analog Computer Serial Output Order)

Wiring

The Computer Serial Port through the straight-through Serial Cable Connected to the RS232 Splitter's Input

The Output Port is also directly Connected to the Device by the straight-through Serial Cable

(That is, the Serial Line 2 to 2,3 to 3 Connected Lines)

At this time the Product can be used as 1 in 4 Out or 1 in 8 Out

Environment

Storage Humidity: 5%-90%RH non- condensing

Ordering Information: 16-Port Gigabit switch

Overview

The TXE018/TXE168 Gigabit Ethernet Switch represents a high-performance, low-cost, simple, seamless

And standardized upgrade that allows you to transform your existing network and achieve 1000Mbps speeds

All 16/24 ports support auto MDI/MDIX, so there is no need to worry about cable types

Simply plug and play

With the innovative energy-efficient technology

TheTXE018/TXE168canreducepower consumption and the vast majority of its packaging material can be recycled

Making it an eco-friendly solution for your business network

Enhanced Performance

All 16/24Ports are Gigabit RJ-45 Ports,allowing them to support large file transfers and makes them compatible with 10Mbps and 100Mbps Ethernet devices

Since both switches feature a non-blocking switching architecture, the TXE018 and TXE168 forward and filter packets at full wire-speed, achieving maximum throughput

10KBJumboframe significantly improves performance during large file transfers IEEE802.3 x flow control supports

Full Duplex mode and back pressure for Half Duplex mode alleviates traffic congestion to make the TXE018/TXE168 more reliable

This makes the TXE018/TXE168 a perfect choice for upgrading your network to Gigabit speed while protecting your previous investment

 Easy of Use

The automated features of this Gigabit switch make installation hassle-free

 No configuration is required. Auto MDI/MDIX eliminates the need for crossover cables

 Auto -negotiation on each port senses the link speed of network devices (10,100, or 1000 Mbps) and intelligently adjusts for compatibility and optimal performance

name: LCD CLEANING KIT
description:
LCD CLEANING KIT - YEC334

Product Manual

A set of three pieces: a brush, a cloth, a bottle of detergent (magic cloth brush cleaning solution)

Professionally wipe the screen, leaving no scratches

Or destroying the liquid crystal surface coating, strong water absorption

Wiping without leaving fluff, strong sterilization effect, Anti-Static effect

Instructions

Fold the edge of the wiping cloth inwards and wipe gently from the center of the LCD screen outwards

However, for stubborn stains, first shake the cleaning agent

About 20-30 cm away from the laptop, LCD Screen, LCD TV Screen

Spray directly on the surface of the screen

Gently wipe it; you can also spray the cleaner directly on the wipe The surface of the cloth

And then wipe the Screen Surface, you can shine as new

The Main Purpose

LCD Screen: It can be used to clean TFT LCD monitors, laptop screens, and PDAs

It can be used with confidence, without hurting the screen coating and leaving no trace of wiping

Household Appliances: It can be used to clean the screens of household appliances such as LCD TVs

Rear Projection TVs, and Plasma TVs

Gently wipe the screen to make it as clean as new

Various Types Of Disc Cleaning: wipe VCD, DVD disc, fold the edge of the bright and clean rag inward

Wipe from the center of the disc to the edge, without leaving fluff and scratches.

Precautions:

Children should not be in contact. Eye contact or swallowing is strictly prohibited

If splashed into eyes, rinse with water

In order to show its decontamination ability.

The experiment was still done on the keyboard that was typed 10,000 times a day

The Keyboard, which was originally very dirty, was indeed clean

When using, the ideal way is to wipe gently in one direction

You can spray on the Screen to wipe

Or you can press the nozzle to spray the clean area of the cleaning cloth for 1 - 2 times to make the cleaning cloth slightly moist

And then wipe the stubborn stains on the screen with the cleaning cloth

After the stubborn stains are wiped off, it is better to repeat

The recommended screen cleaning and maintenance cycle is 2 - 3 days / time
